  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个FinTech系统的核心组件流转图。核心服务是LedgerService，但它需要经过认证和风控才能最终闭环。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FinTech_LedgerService"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，LedgerService是起点。我注意到您提到了认证和风控，AuthVault和FraudDetection这两个组件需要包含进来吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FinTech_AuthVault",
        "FinTech_FraudDetection"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，正是这两个。流程应该是：LedgerService先经过一次内部状态转换，然后进入AuthVault做身份认证，再到FraudDetection做风控检测，最后回到LedgerService完成记账。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FinTech_LedgerService",
        "FinTech_AuthVault",
        "FinTech_FraudDetection"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我理解了，从左到右的流向。为了表达清晰，我在LedgerService内部加一个中间节点B，表示第一次状态转换，然后C节点承接进入AuthVault。这样结构会更清楚。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "B",
        "C",
        "FinTech_LedgerService",
        "FinTech_AuthVault"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "可以，B和C作为过渡节点没问题。从C到AuthVault，然后AuthVault出来到FraudDetection，这两个之间我也需要一个过渡节点D。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "C",
        "D",
        "FinTech_AuthVault",
        "FinTech_FraudDetection"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我现在画出来：A是LedgerService起点，连到B，B连到C，C进入AuthVault，AuthVault通过D连到FraudDetection。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "A",
        "B",
        "C",
        "D",
        "FinTech_LedgerService",
        "FinTech_AuthVault",
        "FinTech_FraudDetection"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，FraudDetection之后还需要一个过渡节点E，然后E再回到LedgerService形成闭环。整个流程是A→B→C→D→E→A。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "E",
        "FinTech_FraudDetection",
        "FinTech_LedgerService"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已加上E节点，FraudDetection通过E回到LedgerService。现在五个节点串联起来了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "E",
        "FinTech_FraudDetection",
