      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "不对，我刚才说错了。C节点应该是AuthVault本身，不是过渡节点。应该是A→B，然后B直接连到AuthVault（就是C），AuthVault再连D到FraudDetection。",
      "elements_involved": [
