      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "明白了，我重新调整：A(LedgerService)→B，B→C(AuthVault)，C→D，D→FraudDetection。这样C就是AuthVault实体了。",
      "elements_involved": [
