    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "清楚了，A和B都是FinTech_LedgerService。最终结构：A(LedgerService)→B(LedgerService)→C(AuthVault)→D→E→回到A。D和E是FraudDetection前后的过渡。",
